ince become.<br><br>   Make adventuring choices that day based on what your character would want to hunt, be it a group of paladins storming the Estate of Unrest, a band of elves trying to unseat Mayong Mistmoore, or a group of Anglers hitting the rivers for a fishing contest and shooting the breeze.  If you play a pirate, skip the spires of Al'Kabor on this day, grab a stack of beers, and ride the boat somewhere <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    If you're playing a shadowknight and that druid friend of yours asks if you want a lift, tell them you'd rather walk then have the little treehugger wisk you around with their cursed Tunarian magic.<br><br>   If you haven't tried roleplaying here before, take this day to work out a personality for your character and go out there and play it.  Surprise all your friends when the level 60 warrior they've been so impressed with all these years confesses that he's deathly afraid of spiders and try and convince the ranger to tank them for you instead <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>   By no means should this be the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  only</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> day people RP, but just a day to try and get everyone on the same page and have some fun not just roleplaying with a few friends, but getting to participate in a server-wide atmospher of roleplay.<br><br>   Spread the word and let your guild/friends know so that even the people who might not visit the boards can still join in on the fun.  <br><br>   Whatcha think?  Good idea?  Lame?  Lemme know <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>- Syll <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usyllestraefv.showPubl